text: Christopher Chace Crawford (born July 18, 1985) is an American actor. He is known for his role as Nate Archibald on The CW's teen drama series Gossip Girl. In 2019, he appeared as the Deep in the Amazon Prime Video original series The Boys. ==Early life== Crawford was born in Lubbock, Texas. His father, Chris, is a dermatologist, and his mother, Dana, is a teacher. He has a younger sister, former Miss Missouri USA winner and Miss USA contestant Candice Crawford. Crawford was raised a Southern Baptist. While his father was a medical student, Chace lived in Bloomington, Minnesota, for four years, attending Ridgeview Elementary School. When his father completed his training, the family moved back to Texas and settled in Plano, a suburb of Dallas. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from Texas Category:People from Lubbock, Texas
